          "settings": {
            "text": "Jordan 9 \"True Red\" Golf Shoe coming 2/23/24",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Get ready to tee off in style with the highly anticipated Jordan 9 \"True Red\" coming soon to TRENDYGOLF. As we dive into the new year, Jordan Brand is giving golfers a reason to get excited by reviving one of its beloved silhouettes. The AJ9 G \"True Red\" is set to make its mark on the green, with official images dropping shortly after professional golfer Pat Perez showcased them on the course.</p><p>While the Jordan 9s have been adapted for golfing in the past, this latest version takes it up a notch. Jordan Brand has swapped out the running midsole for a design that closely resembles the iconic basketball version. Similar to the Air Jordan 6 Low G, which made a triumphant return to the golf scene last year, this iteration stays true to the classic \"True Red\" colorway, with a sleek black mudguard adding a touch of gloss. Underneath, removable spikes and a TPU traction pattern ensure you stay grounded and in control on the fairways.</p><p>Keep your eyes peeled for the release date, expected to drop in the coming weeks at a retail price of $230 USD. With both core and limited colorways on the horizon, the Jordan 9 \"True Red\" promises to elevate your golf game as the season unfolds. Stay tuned for more updates and be ready to hit the course in style.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
